comments: Gallinari (LAC) lifts his left pivot foot before the start of his dribble.
Love (CLE) makes leg to leg contact with Gallinari (LAC) during Gallinari's drive to the basket that affects his SQBR.
Osman (CLE) makes brief contact with Williams's (LAC) arm as he tries to establish position.
Gallinari (LAC) slightly extends his arms into Love (CLE), who is still able to reach his desired position on the floor.
Osman (CLE) extends his arm into Gallinari (LAC) and dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Clarkson (CLE) and does not deliver the contact.
RAR shows Beverley (LAC) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Sexton (CLE) that does not affect his SQBR.
Love (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Williams (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Beverley (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Clarkson (CLE) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gallinari (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Sexton (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Clarkson (CLE) makes marginal contact with Williams (LAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
Nance Jr. (CLE) makes incidental contact with Harrell (LAC) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beverley (LAC) and does not deliver any contact.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Harrell (LAC) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Gallinari (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Love (CLE) that does not affect his post move and shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) makes contact with Shamet (LAC) that affects his SQBR once he has secured the loose ball.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thornwell (LAC) and does not deliver the contact.
Osman (CLE) attempts to commit a take foul on Beverley (LAC) but the contact is marginal.
Clarkson (CLE) has a hand placed on Beverley's (LAC) back but he does not push him or otherwise dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Beverley (LAC).
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Gallinari (LAC) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Love (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thornwell (LAC) with his arms collapsed and does not deliver contact.
Thornwell (LAC) and Clarkson (CLE) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Gallinari (LAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Clarkson (CLE) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
